# Harness fixture only, not part of what setup-graph-hooks installs. This fixture exists to
# carry a real, prebuilt graph so the grader can prove the wired hooks actually steer a
# search — so its graph is source, and must be committed. A nested .gitignore beats the repo
# root's negation, so the re-include has to live here.
!.code-review-graph/
!graphify-out/
!.claude/settings.local.json
